{
  "stem": "2316.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the nap, we would take a walk to the park.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Jewish people would meet there and sit, and gossip and whatnot, talk politics, and small talk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the children would play together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the synagogue it was-- it was very chauvinistic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it was just men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Women really didn't have any say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- they were not important at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were just-- they were the enablers, the supporters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were very Orthodox, like I say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was a very, very Orthodox child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was the most Orthodox person in my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother would comb her hair on Shabbos, I would squeal on her to my dad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I would say, Mom combed her-- I was so upset.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It would upset me to no end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I thought, you know, she would drop dead for doing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if my brother would do a little homework or break a stick or something, I-- I would be squealing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I would hit him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I would be so upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'd cry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was worried about him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But my mother wasn't-- I was a fanatic, because-- I don't know, I was taught that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I figured, what is it-- that's what you're supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They broke the law as far as I was concerned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So-- but most of the shtetl, 95% were like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the other synagogue was a little more elite.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a brick-- a brick building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The only brick building that I remember in the shtetl was that other synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they had a chevra kadisha.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They-- they really did a lot for small town, in a poor little shtetl like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They accomplished a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They would bring poor people in for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
